{
  "dialogue": {
    "Ooh!... I can read it on your face. You're going to love it here in Pelican Town.": [
      "Introduction"
    ],
    "If you're ever looking for something to do in the evening, stop by the saloon. That's where I work!": [
      "Introduction_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh, you remembered my birthday! Thanks, @! That's  really nice of you.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive"
    ],
    "Oh, you remembered my birthday! T hanks, @! That's really ni--": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative"
    ],
    "...*sniff*...*sniff*... what is that smell?": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative_sv1"
    ],
    "... What is this...?": ["AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative_sv2"],
    "Yes, I'd love to dance with you, @!": ["FlowerDance_Accept"],
    "Now I'm excited... This is going to be a lot of fun!": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept_sv1"
    ],
    "Wow, thank you! I've heard that if you drink this before bed you'll have vivid dreams.": [
      "AcceptGift_StardropTea"
    ],
    "Oh, good, it's still warm... Poor thing, where's it's mother? *Whisper* ...I'll be your mother, don't worry... Poor baby.": [
      "AcceptGift_ParrotEgg"
    ],
    "I'm glad you gave this to me, @. I'll take very good care of it.": [
      "AcceptGift_ParrotEgg_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh, wow... Thank you! This color perfectly captures my mood today.": [
      "AcceptGift_68_chance_1"
    ],
    "The warm, soothing energy of this stone helps us re-center our thoughts... It's actually just what I needed on a day like this. Thanks!": [
      "AcceptGift_68_chance_2"
    ],
    "That's funny, I had a dream that you would give me a piece of jade today!": [
      "AcceptGift_70_chance_1"
    ],
    "Ooh, it's jade! This is supposed to attract wealth... And who couldn't do with a few extra coins in the pocket?": [
      "AcceptGift_70_chance_2"
    ],
    "Oh, it's beautiful, @! I hope you didn't put yourself in too much danger to get this.": [
      "AcceptGift_66_chance_1"
    ],
    "Ah, an amethyst! This will protect me on those late nights working at the Saloon.": [
      "AcceptGift_66_chance_2"
    ],
    "Wow, look at that color! It matches perfectly with my outfit.": [
      "AcceptGift_64_chance_1"
    ],
    "Oh, this is perfect... I've been feeling a little sluggish lately. Rubies are great for energizing the spirit!": [
      "AcceptGift_64_chance_2"
    ],
    "It's so smooth! When I hold it... I can feel the energy of all the mermaids in the sea. Thank you!": [
      "AcceptGift_62_chance_1"
    ],
    "Thank you! I'm gonna put this under my pillow, and hopefully I'll dream about the ocean.": [
      "AcceptGift_62_chance_2"
    ],
    "Oh!... Heheh... I know exactly why you gave me this stone today. Very interesting...": [
      "AcceptGift_60_chance_1"
    ],
    "Wow, it's beautiful! This color makes me think of all the spiritual power within the forest... Can you feel that wood energy?": [
      "AcceptGift_60_chance_2"
    ],
    "There must be a meaning behind this... Nature is trying to tell us something.": [
      "GreenRain"
    ],
    "What, though? I can't tell... It's hard to read. I feel a strong presence, though...": [
      "GreenRain_sv1"
    ],
    "Can you feel it? The forest is singing! The trees are dancing with joy!": [
      "GreenRain_2"
    ],
    "That was a beautiful wedding... I'm really happy for you and Haley!": [
      "married_Haley"
    ],
    "Haley is too proud to be heartbroken over the divorce... Or at least to show it.": [
      "divorced_Haley"
    ],
    "Hello @. I had a feeling I'd be seeing you today.": ["eventSeen_471942"],
    "Nothing is more sad than an injured animal...": ["eventSeen_463391"],
    "Now that you have a sheep, you'll be able to make cloth! That'll open up a whole new world of tailoring possibilities. Just wait and see.": [
      "purchasedAnimal_Sheep"
    ],
    "Have you ever tried cooking without a recipe? It's kind of liberating.": [
      "eventSeen_11_memory_oneweek"
    ],
    "And who knows... you might discover something amazing!": [
      "eventSeen_11_memory_oneweek_sv1"
    ],
    "My outing with Clint was pretty fun!": ["eventSeen_101_memory_oneweek"],
    "Although, he spilled a root beer all over himself within ten minutes of getting there, and then barely said a word the rest of the night.": [
      "eventSeen_101_memory_oneweek_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey, I saw you at Sam's show. It was fun!": ["eventSeen_4081148"],
    "The city smelled pretty bad, though.": ["eventSeen_4081148_sv1"],
    "I won't forget our camping trip any time soon...": [
      "eventSeen_2123343_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "%Emily has a big smile on her face.": ["dating_Emily"],
    "We're going to have a lot of fun together, I just know it.": [
      "dating_Emily_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "Well, now that you're married, I assume Shane won't be coming to the Saloon as much!": [
      "married_Shane"
    ],
    "That's probably a good thing, but it's always a little sad to lose a regular...": [
      "married_Shane_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh, I like this place! It's full of parrots!": ["Resort_Entering"],
    "Ah... my lungs feel perfect.": ["Resort_Leaving"],
    "Can you feel it? The ocean has a profound healing energy.": [
      "Resort_Shore"
    ],
    "Are you having fun, @? You need to remember to take breaks now and then too!": [
      "Resort_Chair"
    ],
    "It's nice to be on this side of the bar for once!": ["Resort_Bar"],
    "If you open your heart to the sun, you can feel a loving energy inside of you.": [
      "Resort"
    ],
    "%Emily is lost in the music.": ["Resort_Dance"],
    "Of course, my love. I've been looking forward to this!": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse"
    ],
    "I'm very sorry... but I've already agreed to dance with someone else.": [
      "FlowerDance_Decline"
    ],
    "@... You broke my heart... I just can't talk to you anymore.": [
      "divorced"
    ],
    "Please, let me try to heal...": ["divorced_sv1"],
    "...": ["dumped_Girls"],
    "B...But I thought we had a special bond... *sniff*": ["breakUp"],
    "Oh, that's beautiful... I have a friend who would love that! But she lives far from here...": [
      "reject_866"
    ],
    "@... I'm ready to give you a second chance. I still have faith that there's a good person inside of you.": [
      "secondChance_Girls"
    ],
    "Have I told you Haley and I are sisters? Strange, isn't it?": ["Mon"],
    "I have a secret hobby, but I won't say any more.": ["Mon2"],
    "Maybe I'll show you some day.": ["Mon2_sv1"],
    "This world is full of spirits and magic... Some don't believe me, but I know it's true.": [
      "Mon4"
    ],
    "I can see it in your eyes... you believe in the other world, like me.": [
      "Mon4_sv1"
    ],
    "I wish Haley would get a job or at least contribute to cooking and cleaning.": [
      "Mon6"
    ],
    "I think she's hoping to marry someone rich.": ["Mon6_sv1"],
    "I have to say, now that Haley's gone I've had a much easier time keeping things in order.": [
      "Mon6_inlaw_Haley"
    ],
    "There's good people in this town who just can't seem to find happiness. It makes me sad.": [
      "Mon8"
    ],
    "Working in the saloon, I hear first-hand about everyone's problems.": [
      "Mon8_sv1"
    ],
    "I work part-time at Gus' saloon. It pays the bills.": ["Tue"],
    "I'm just working at Gus' to make ends meet... but my real passion is tailoring.": [
      "Tue4"
    ],
    "I made these clothes from scratch, see?": ["Tue4_sv1"],
    "Oh, hi... It's nice of you to visit me like this.": ["Tue6"],
    "You know, @... I think the future looks bright for both of us.": ["Tue8"],
    "I've heard rumors of rare and powerful magic rings, forged long ago by forgotten civilizations. I'm not sure if it's true or just a fairy tale.": [
      "Wed"
    ],
    "You catch fish? I just hope you treat the poor things humanely.": ["Wed4"],
    "Every critter deserves our respect, even the slimy ones.": ["Wed4_sv1"],
    "Have faith... every day you're taking one more step on the path of your destiny.": [
      "Wed6"
    ],
    "Hey, @.": ["Wed8_query_1"],
    "I always knew we would become good friends. It was written in the stars!": [
      "Wed8_query_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Hi, @.": ["Wed8_query_2"],
    "I always knew we'd become close like this...": ["Wed8_query_2_sv1"],
    "I hope you're farming in a sustainable way. The valley's ecosystem is fragile!": [
      "Thu"
    ],
    "How do I know? I have a strong gut-feeling!": ["Thu_sv1"],
    "Sometimes the flowers speak to me... each one has a different story to tell!": [
      "Thu4"
    ],
    "Ah, spring. The season of pastels. I actually prefer jewel tones, myself.": [
      "Fri"
    ],
    "Oh, excuse me! I was mumbling about fashion again, wasn't I?": ["Fri_sv1"],
    "I like making my own clothes, but it's not easy to get cloth.": ["Sat"],
    "And it's such a long trip to the city.": ["Sat_sv1"],
    "Do you ever think about the texture of fabric, @? Each texture has a distinct personality... feel my dress... see?": [
      "Sat6"
    ],
    "Hi @!": ["Sun", "summer_Sun"],
    "Do you raise sheep in your barn? You can turn their wool into beautiful bolts of cloth!": [
      "Sun_sv1"
    ],
    "You'll need a loom, though. You can make them yourself if you know the crafting recipe.": [
      "Sun_sv2"
    ],
    "This house was left in our care by my parents. The  y've been traveling the world for the last two years.": [
      "Sun4"
    ],
    "We have no idea when they'll be back.": ["Sun4_sv1"],
    "I enjoy living here, though. It's a beautiful area and the town is nice.": [
      "Sun4_sv2"
    ],
    "Thank you!": ["event_dance1"],
    "Um... Okay. Sorry you didn't like it. I guess those three years of practice were a complete waste...": [
      "event_dance2"
    ],
    "Did you really think so? That's exactly the effect I was shooting for!": [
      "event_dance3"
    ],
    "I'm so glad you liked it.": ["event_dance3_sv1"],
    "Haley is a picky eater. It's so hard to cook for her.": ["summer_Mon"],
    "Eating healthy is very important to me. I want to live a long and active life.": [
      "summer_Mon4"
    ],
    "Haley and I get along much better now that she's moved out. I look forward to her visits!": [
      "summer_Mon_inlaw_Haley"
    ],
    "Hello there, @.": ["summer_Tue"],
    "I feel lazy today.": ["summer_Tue_sv1"],
    "I feel bad for Linus. People judge him, but he's just living a different lifestyle.": [
      "summer_Tue6"
    ],
    "I wish everyone could learn to be accepting of others.": [
      "summer_Tue6_sv1"
    ],
    "Hi, @! We've become decent friends, haven't we?": [
      "summer_Sun6",
      "summer_Sun8"
    ],
    "That's fine with me. You're a cool guy.": ["summer_Sun6_sv1_male_farmer"],
    "I'm glad.": ["summer_Sun6_sv1_female_farmer"],
    "This may sound weird, but I've always been certain this would happen.": [
      "summer_Sun8_sv1"
    ],
    "It doesn't rain much in summer, does it?": ["summer_Wed"],
    "That just means more watering work for you, huh?": ["summer_Wed_sv1"],
    "Or do you enjoy the sunny weather?": ["summer_Wed_sv2"],
    "I consider the bees and butterflies to be my special friends!": [
      "summer_Thu"
    ],
    "If I wasn't so busy I'd come help you on the farm!": ["summer_Fri"],
    "But Gus would be upset if I had another job...": ["summer_Fri_sv1"],
    "You know, I'm sure Gus would understand if I wanted to leave the Saloon someday.": [
      "summer_Fri6"
    ],
    "There's so much out there, I can't stay a barmaid forever.": [
      "summer_Fri6_sv1"
    ],
    "Don't overwork yourself or you might end up in Harvey's clinic!": [
      "summer_Sat"
    ],
    "It's around this time of year that my good friends visit the region... I mean the parrots!": [
      "summer_Sun4"
    ],
    "Well, fall is here. Time to plant some new crops, huh?": ["fall_1"],
    "I'm visiting Sandy today. We're best friends!": ["fall_15_prereq_1"],
    "I'm really happy that the bus is repaired.": ["fall_15_prereq_1_sv1"],
    "*Sigh*... If only that old bus were fixed, I would've visited my friend Sandy today...": [
      "fall_15_prereq_2"
    ],
    "It's good weather for a picnic, isn't it?": ["fall_Mon"],
    "If I didn't have to work I'd suggest we go on a nice picnic!": [
      "fall_Mon8"
    ],
    "Hello. Did you have a good summer?": ["fall_Tue"],
    "Hi @! I bet your farm did great this past summer, huh?": ["fall_Tue4"],
    "You're an excellent farmer.": ["fall_Tue4_sv1"],
    "My friend runs a shop in the desert. If you ever go there stop in and say hi for me.": [
      "fall_Wed"
    ],
    "I think she sells some rare products.": ["fall_Wed_sv1"],
    "Are you friends with Clint? He's a nice guy, if you get to know him.": [
      "fall_Thu"
    ],
    "He gets lonely working in his shop all day. But he's so shy he has trouble making new friends.": [
      "fall_Thu_sv1"
    ],
    "I think Clint's mad at me. He never looks at me anymore...": ["fall_Thu8"],
    "I always thought we were friends.": ["fall_Thu8_sv1"],
    "Another beautiful fall day.": ["fall_Fri"],
    "It's a pity it'll soon be over.": ["fall_Fri_sv1"],
    "Smell that clean air? It's lovely, isn't it?": ["fall_Fri6"],
    "I just fear that the Joja Co.'s of the world will take this away from us.": [
      "fall_Fri6_sv1"
    ],
    "Keep your mind open and some interesting things might take root.": [
      "fall_Sat"
    ],
    "Anyway, how is your day going?": ["fall_Sat_sv1"],
    "I don't have any huge plans for life. I prefer not to stress about the future.": [
      "fall_Sat6"
    ],
    "Nothing like a sunny Sunday to lift the spirits!": ["fall_Sun"],
    "There's so many invisible barriers holding us back. Why can't people learn to let go and explore their true potential?": [
      "fall_Sun6"
    ],
    "Me? Well, you know what they say... 'You can't cage a wild Junimo'.": [
      "fall_Sun6_sv1"
    ],
    "You're such a nice person, @! Thanks for being my friend.": ["fall_Sun10"],
    "Be careful an icicle doesn't fall on your head!": ["winter_Mon"],
    "Be careful an icicle doesn't fall on your head! I wouldn't want you to get hurt!": [
      "winter_Mon10"
    ],
    "Oh, hello @!": ["winter_Tue"],
    "You must be getting very good at farming by now, huh?": ["winter_Tue_sv1"],
    "I bet you're an excellent farmer by now!": ["winter_Tue2"],
    "I think my hair is frozen solid...": ["winter_Tue4"],
    "Haley and I aren't made for such a big house. It's a hassle to keep it clean.": [
      "winter_Wed"
    ],
    "Ah well. I really shouldn't be complaining.": ["winter_Wed_sv1"],
    "Your farmhouse seems nice and cozy.": ["winter_Wed_sv2"],
    "It must be so cold for the poor fish.": ["winter_Thu"],
    "I wonder if any fish hibernate? Maybe I should ask Demetrius.": [
      "winter_Thu_sv1"
    ],
    "If I wasn't so busy I'd help you dig around in that cave by the lake.": [
      "winter_Fri"
    ],
    "I bet there are some powerful crystals inside there.": ["winter_Fri_sv1"],
    "Do you know how to cook 'Bean Hotpot'?": ["winter_Sat"],
    "I like that dish quite a bit.%revealtaste:Emily:207": ["winter_Sat_sv1"],
    "It's hard to get fresh ingredients in the winter, huh?": [
      "winter_Sat_sv2"
    ],
    "Hi!": ["winter_Sun"],
    "...Yes?": ["winter_Sun_sv1"],
    "My sister and I might fight sometimes, but I would really miss her if she left.": [
      "winter_Sun6"
    ],
    "I think she'll become a very nice young lady some day... Don't tell her I said that.": [
      "winter_Sun6_sv1"
    ],
    "So, is there anything you want to talk about?": ["winter_Sun6_sv2"],
    "Say hi to my sister for me! And remind her to visit me tomorrow.": [
      "winter_Sun6_inlaw_Haley"
    ]
  },
  "marriage_dialogue": {
    "I wonder where the flying insects go when it rains? Don't they get hit by the raindrops?": [
      "Rainy_Day_0"
    ],
    "A day like this is a blessing from mother nature.": ["Rainy_Day_1"],
    "Good morning... I got this gift for you. Don't worry, I already purified it with sage incense.": [
      "Rainy_Day_2"
    ],
    "I meant to let the parrot go free, but his wing never fully healed. He seems content, though. I give him lots of attention.": [
      "Rainy_Day_3"
    ],
    "He told me that he's happy here.": ["Rainy_Day_3_sv1"],
    "I never told you this... but when you first moved here I had a dream about you. I knew right then that our life-paths would intertwine.": [
      "Rainy_Day_4"
    ],
    "Every moment has a unique and precious beauty... do you notice? It can be easy to forget, sometimes.": [
      "Rainy_Night_0"
    ],
    "This is my favorite spot for a morning meditation.": ["patio_Emily"],
    "I visualize the energy from this crystal garden flowing through my body.": [
      "patio_Emily_sv1"
    ],
    "I can hear the plants talking to each other... they're so happy after today's rain!": [
      "Rainy_Night_1"
    ],
    "How was your day, @? You look a little soggy.": ["Rainy_Night_2"],
    "My day was very peaceful. How was yours?": ["Rainy_Night_3"],
    "Want some dessert? It's my special raw, gluten-free version, sweetened only with cactus syrup.": [
      "Rainy_Night_4"
    ],
    "Does the sound of rain ever put you in a trance?": ["Rainy_Night_5"],
    "Another beautiful day on %farm farm... I have faith that something good will happen today!": [
      "Indoor_Day_0"
    ],
    "Here, take this. It's for you.": ["Indoor_Day_1"],
    "Hey, someone must've gotten a good night of sleep... you look fresh this morning.": [
      "Indoor_Day_2"
    ],
    "My horoscope for the day isn't too good... but I'm going to make the best of it, as always. Let's get to work!": [
      "Indoor_Day_3"
    ],
    "Ughh... *gurgle*... I ate too many bran muffins for breakfast.": [
      "Indoor_Day_4"
    ],
    "Is that a new hole I see in your shirt? I can sew that up for you, no problem.": [
      "Indoor_Night_0"
    ],
    "Welcome home, @. I hope you had a wonderful day.": ["Indoor_Night_1"],
    "Is it bed time already? My, the day just floated away from me again.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2"
    ],
    "Ah, that aroma! It can only be you.": ["Indoor_Night_3"],
    "It's a good smell.": ["Indoor_Night_3_sv1"],
    "I swept the whole house, washed the windows, dusted, and cleaned the fridge. It was a very productive day!": [
      "Indoor_Night_4"
    ],
    "I love getting up early. There's a certain freshness to the air and the wildlife is much more active.": [
      "Outdoor_0"
    ],
    "What's on the agenda today, dear?": ["Outdoor_1"],
    "Oooh! Ooh! I saw another one!": ["Outdoor_2"],
    "I'm counting squirrels.": ["Outdoor_2_sv1"],
    "A little sunlight is good for you. Just don't get crispy, okay?": [
      "Outdoor_3"
    ],
    "Good morning! I was wondering when you'd finally roll out of bed!": [
      "Outdoor_4"
    ],
    "It's okay, @... you deserve a good night of rest.": ["Outdoor_4_sv1"],
    "I hope we can raise %kid1 to be kind and considerate. That's more important than getting A's in school.": [
      "OneKid_0"
    ],
    "Is one child enough, or should we raise another?": ["OneKid_1"],
    "I guess we'll just see where fate leads us.": ["OneKid_1_sv1"],
    "I lit a pale green candle and shook a sprig of baby-mint over %kid1. That should ward off any dangerous spirits.": [
      "OneKid_3"
    ],
    "A big house, two kids and a parrot... I have my hands full!": [
      "TwoKids_1"
    ],
    "Well, %kid2 certainly has your hair...": ["TwoKids_2"],
    "Oh, I already fed the kids their organic quinoa puffs with goat milk. You just focus on the farm!": [
      "TwoKids_3"
    ],
    "This is so fun to live together! I always thought I'd be single my whole life.": [
      "Good_1"
    ],
    "It was our destiny to be together... I believe that with all my heart!": [
      "Good_2"
    ],
    "Thanks for taking me into your home. I love this new life.": ["Good_3"],
    "Our vibrational energies are perfectly in tune. Can't you feel it?": [
      "Good_4"
    ],
    "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... The shell is beautiful! I can feel the pure blue energy radiating from it.": [
      "Good_5"
    ],
    "I had another dream about us last night. We had climbed to the top of a crystal tree, looking down on the most lush and beautiful meadow. I keep having this dream.": [
      "Good_6"
    ],
    "I don't know what it means, but I feel that it's a good omen.": [
      "Good_6_sv1"
    ],
    "I hope you'll still like me when I grow old and my hair turns to a dull, faded steel.": [
      "Neutral_0"
    ],
    "I feel uninspired today.": ["Neutral_8"],
    "I'm going to visit town today, and later on I'm going to help out at the saloon. Have a nice day.": [
      "funLeave_Emily"
    ],
    "My day went well... it's good to get out of the house now and then.": [
      "funReturn_Emily"
    ],
    "My friends, the plants, have come back to life. I feel content.": [
      "spring_2"
    ],
    "Happy new year, honey. Let's make this a special one.": ["spring_1"],
    "Hmm... I'm thinking maybe a salad of fresh foraged greens for dinner tonight?": [
      "spring_22"
    ],
    "The energy in our bodies fluctuate just as the seasons do. Understanding your own unique rhythm is the first step to inner harmony.": [
      "summer_20"
    ],
    "May Yoba bless you on this lovely day.": ["summer_2"],
    "The year's already half-way over. Can you believe it?": ["fall_1"],
    "Our bodies are naturally in tune with the seasons. This light and color of fall compels us to prepare for the barren winter.": [
      "fall_25"
    ],
    "To our distant ancestors, this feeling was encompassing and vital. For us, it only barely peeks through the noise of modern life.": [
      "fall_25_sv1"
    ],
    "On a day like this, I have a craving for cinnamon, nutmeg, clove, and cardamom.": [
      "winter_15"
    ],
    "*sigh*... Why does there have to be war and hatred in the world?": [
      "winter_5"
    ],
    "I can't help but think of all the poor, frozen squirrels out there right now.": [
      "winter_2"
    ],
    "I'm feeling excited for a new year of farming, @!": ["spring_Emily"],
    "I drank a super-food smoothie this morning and I feel aaah-mazing!": [
      "fall_Emily"
    ],
    "Phew! It's hot but it feels great, doesn't it?": ["summer_Emily"],
    "Maybe we'll see some wild parrots today.": ["summer_Emily_sv1"],
    "Whoops, my hair is frozen solid again.": ["winter_Emily"],
    "I'm going to spend some time with the parrot today. It breaks my heart that he'll never fly again.": [
      "spouseRoom_Emily"
    ]
  },
  "gift_tastes": {
    "This gift is fabulous! Thank you so much!": ["EmilyGiftTaste_1"],
    "Thank you! I'm feeling a positive energy from this gift.": [
      "EmilyGiftTaste_2"
    ],
    "Thanks!": ["EmilyGiftTaste_3"],
    "Sorry... I don't like this.": ["EmilyGiftTaste_4"],
    "This gift has a strong negative energy. I can't stand it.": [
      "EmilyGiftTaste_5"
    ]
  },
  "misc": {
    "You're looking great!": ["MakeOver_Emily_AlreadyStyled"],
    "Come back another day and we'll put together a fresh new look for you!": [
      "MakeOver_Emily_AlreadyStyled_sv1"
    ],
    "Hmm, your backpack's looking a little full. Come back when you've made enough room for a full set of clothes!": [
      "MakeOver_Emily_InventoryFull"
    ],
    "Okay, before we continue, let me visualize your aura, to see what kind of style will make you happiest...": [
      "MakeOver_Emily_1"
    ],
    "Yes... I see...": ["MakeOver_Emily_2"],
